### Run Bert Ensemble Inference
POST http://localhost:8080/infer/
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: test-key

{
  "model_name": "bert_ensemble",
  "inputs": {
    "texts": [
      "Artificial intelligence is transforming the world.",
      "The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog.",
      "A large language model trained on diverse data.",
      "The cat sat on the mat.",
      "Machine learning enables predictive analytics."
    ]
  }
}

### Run LLM Generate
POST http://localhost:8080/generate
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: test-key

{
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Explain what TensorRT is in 2 sentences."}
  ],
  "max_tokens": 128,
  "temperature": 0.7
}

### Run LLM Generate (Streaming)
POST http://localhost:8080/generate
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: test-key

{
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Count from 1 to 10."}
  ],
  "max_tokens": 64,
  "stream": true
}

### Run CLIP Ensemble Inference
POST http://localhost:8080/infer/
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: test-key

{
  "model_name": "clip_ensemble",
  "inputs": {
    "image_urls": [
      "https://picsum.photos/id/237/512/512",
      "https://picsum.photos/id/1025/512/512",
      "https://picsum.photos/id/1003/512/512",
      "https://picsum.photos/id/1018/512/512",
      "https://picsum.photos/id/1020/512/512"
    ],
    "texts": [
      "a photo of a cat",
      "a small bird",
      "a golden retriever dog",
      "a red flower",
      "a yellow sunflower"
    ]
  }
}
